The magazine is packed with feel-good reading, including seven original short stories by favourite authors, and two exclusive serial instalments. There’s a new episode of the much-loved soap, “Riverside”, by bestselling author Glenda Young, the latest slice of rural life in beautiful Dorset from columnist Maddie Grigg and ahost of interesting and informative features to brighten your day. And if that wasn’t enough, get practical gardening hints and tips from regular columnist Alexandra Campbell as well as puzzles and brainteasers to keep your mind active. The “Friend” is the perfect companion to spend an hour or two with – just sit back, put your feet up and relax! So be sure to pick up your Daily Express or Sunday Express this weekend (May 7 or 8, 2022) where you'll find the voucher you'll need to redeem the offer in-store.